37:04.523 --> 37:07.958
            Then do it yourself.

37:09.261 --> 37:11.428
I can find someone else.

37:11.430 --> 37:12.963
     Just... Don't... Just stop.

37:12.965 --> 37:15.966
               Take another step
                  and i swear...

37:15.968 --> 37:18.235
    You swear?

37:18.670 --> 37:19.970
You swear what?

37:21.340 --> 37:22.939
You won't kill me.

37:22.941 --> 37:25.508
Because killing me

37:25.510 --> 37:27.677
Kills your son.

37:29.314 --> 37:32.649
It kills the only possibility
of ever seeing him again.

37:37.422 --> 37:38.989
    I am...

37:38.991 --> 37:41.258
     Your only hope.

37:50.569 --> 37:52.702
        Don't be scared.

37:52.704 --> 37:54.571
     I'm not.

37:54.573 --> 37:56.640
Good, i didn't
think so.

37:56.642 --> 37:58.675
      You're pretty tough.

37:58.677 --> 38:00.677
                  My brother has
                   a little girl

38:00.679 --> 38:03.480
         Just like you.
       Her name's nadia.

38:03.482 --> 38:05.382
Where are we going?

38:05.384 --> 38:06.616
       Honey, don't talk to him.

38:06.618 --> 38:07.984
     Why not?

38:11.923 --> 38:13.590
            Houston.

38:13.592 --> 38:15.458
We're gonna
go to houston.

38:15.460 --> 38:17.027
   That's lucky.

38:17.029 --> 38:18.495
         That's lucky?

38:18.497 --> 38:20.430
         Honey, don't.

38:20.432 --> 38:22.699
We were going there anyway.
It's lucky you picked us.

38:22.701 --> 38:24.567
       Amy, what did i just say?

38:24.569 --> 38:26.636
             Stop talking to him
            and do your drawing.

38:33.645 --> 38:36.479
Why are you going to houston?

38:37.649 --> 38:39.616
      Nadia and her daddy
        are in houston.

38:41.420 --> 38:43.486
Need to make sure they're okay.

38:49.628 --> 38:51.027
You on the run, buddy?

38:51.029 --> 38:52.362
            No, sir.

38:52.364 --> 38:55.365
I believe you. Why not?

38:55.367 --> 38:56.866
Houston all right?

38:56.868 --> 38:58.335
       Sounds good to me.

38:58.337 --> 38:59.502
Come on,
let's go.

39:12.684 --> 39:14.918
            The man:
     <i> Vera, you experienced</i>

39:14.920 --> 39:17.787
          <i> Things today</i>
     <i> you don't understand.</i>

39:17.789 --> 39:20.490
   <i> You're trying to deny it,</i>

39:20.492 --> 39:22.559
        <i> But you feel it.</i>

39:24.596 --> 39:26.429
       <i> Nothing is random.</i>

39:26.431 --> 39:30.600
   <i> Nothing is a coincidence.</i>

39:30.602 --> 39:33.436
    <i> Everything is happening</i>
         <i> for a reason.</i>

39:33.438 --> 39:38.007
          <i> And you have</i>
   <i> an important part to play.</i>

39:43.949 --> 39:46.750
          (whooshing)

40:13.011 --> 40:15.545
         (horn blares)

40:15.547 --> 40:17.881
       Driver: Hey, you can't...
           (honking)

40:17.883 --> 40:19.783
                       Driver 2:
        Come on, buddy, come on.

40:19.785 --> 40:21.451
            I died.

40:21.453 --> 40:23.520
       And yet here i am.

40:26.024 --> 40:27.157
              Why?

40:27.159 --> 40:30.026
     (honking in distance)

40:30.028 --> 40:32.095
     I bring you a warning.

40:32.931 --> 40:35.732
   The devil is here with us,

40:35.734 --> 40:37.801
      In flesh and blood.

40:39.638 --> 40:43.606
      He knows our secrets
         and our fears.

40:43.608 --> 40:47.076
And he will use them against us.

40:47.078 --> 40:50.046
   He is temptation and sin.

40:50.048 --> 40:53.016
     He is evil incarnate.

40:53.018 --> 40:55.084
         He is lucifer,

40:55.086 --> 40:58.021
    The prince of darkness.

40:58.023 --> 41:00.056
  And i am here to tell you--

41:00.058 --> 41:03.793
Whether you believe it or not--

41:03.795 --> 41:07.931
    He is coming for us all.

